{
  "stem": "8359.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I guess this German woman, she must have, you know, known some about-- about Judaism.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She wouldn't eat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was so thin that I can't begin to tell you, because she wouldn't do or eat a lot of stuff because it was treif.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you know that she told her, that Yom Kippur, she says, don't go in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll-- I'll-- I'll say you're sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Stay in-- stay on-- stay in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't go into work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's something to be believed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were a few of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I got to go ahead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because everything that I am telling you now-- this was like-- like you would call a resort almost.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That-- that-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the 1943, we were transferred.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, that part of Sudeten, every couple of miles there was a factory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a factory that was call-- oh, oh, oh, I forgot to tell you that we weren't the original 90, because they kept sending more girl--",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to get transports come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To us, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then it also already was getting harder, because even though she was good to us, but as the-- as it was getting bigger, she had to have an assistant, and she had to be more careful, you know.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only women, only women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never saw a Jewish man till 1945.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'll get to that, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This Haase, which is spelled H-A-A-S-E, was another textile factory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They started a few months later than we did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had a woman, just like ours was good, that's how miserable she was, a real, real Nazi, Jew-hater.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they transferred us there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took us out-- not out of the factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We still worked in the Walzel factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, on foot.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
